      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JULY SHE LIED (1) filled a minor placing last start at Traralgon behind Daintree Damage (24.42) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Likely to feature again. CACKLING SUZIE (2) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at Warrnambool in a handy 25.70 beating Blue Brebler. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Sure to measure up. CHAPPY'S TOTEM (8) was drawn the middle last start but pinged the lids and recorded an all-the-way win (26.22) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 460m. Won at his only start from this box. Should feature again. ON THE RIVER (7) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
